      body2: 'AI offers a genuine opportunity here — not to replace clinical judgment, but to dramatically reduce the administrative and cognitive burden that makes clinical work unsustainable. The organizations that use AI to give clinicians time back may find that they can retain, attract, and develop talent in ways that organizations treating AI as a cost reduction tool cannot.',
